overview: The user wanted to elevate the visual appeal of their sleep
  questionnaire app, moving it beyond a generic look to something more
  professional and calming. The assistant began by thoroughly reviewing the
  existing design, identifying areas for improvement in color, typography,
  layout, and form elements. A new sleep-themed color palette was introduced,
  along with custom gradients and shadows. Key components like the main
  questionnaire form, progress bar, intro section, and report section were
  redesigned with subtle decorative elements, improved visual hierarchy, and
  enhanced user feedback. Form fields like checkboxes, radio buttons, and
  sliders also received significant styling updates. The outcome is a visually
  cohesive and engaging application that better reflects its purpose as a sleep
  health assessment tool.
